   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="da_br_k_282_1"/>Ab<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ender: Karl Kraus, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb1178">I.
                     Maximilian<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tr 13</rs>.</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine>Loris</addrLine><addrLine>Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine>Beer-Hofmann</addrLine></address><address><addrLine>Herrn</addrLine><addrLine>Richard Dehmel</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb17871">Pankow bei Berlin</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43459">Parkstr. 25.</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline><pb facs="da_br_k_282_2"/><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>, <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00297-1"/><date>10. II. 93</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00297-1">Die Datierung ist, wie aus den
                     Poststempeln ersichtlich wird, um ein Jahr falsch.</note>.</dateline></opener><p><rs type="place" ref="#pmb262">Café Central</rs> – die Secession<add place="inline">isten</add> der Secession (<hi rend="underline" n="1">nicht mehr</hi> das altberühmte <rs type="place" ref="#pmb34">Café Grien<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>teidl</rs> oder »Steinkrügl«, wie <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12071">Liliencron</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>agt)</p><p>Lieb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ter Dehmel, viele<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chöne Grüße, Sie welttiefer Völkerpsycholog. Meinen Brief
               haben Sie wohl<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon!</p><p>Gruß an <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10928">Bierbaum</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12664">Schlaf</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="#pmb5666">Scheerbart</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11565">Halbe</rs>! Ihr <signed>Karl Kraus.</signed></p><p><signed><handShift scribe="#pmb11740"/>Richard Beer-Hofmann<note xml:id="FN_00297_1" type="footnote"><p><bibl><rs type="work" ref="#pmb32832">Novellen</rs>. <rs type="place" ref="#pmb168">Berlin</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="org" ref="#pmb39772">Freund <c rendition="#kaufmannsund"/>
                              Jäckel</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>1893</date></bibl></p></note><note xml:id="FN_00297_2" type="footnote"><p>dieser Dichter hat nicht selbst unterschrieben, weil er nicht schreiben kann
                        aber er sitzt auch da. Loris.</p></note></signed></p><p><signed>Loris</signed></p><p><handShift scribe="#pmb2121"/>Herzliche Grüße <signed>Arthur Schnitzler</signed></p></div>
      </body>
